The '''borrat''' was a large, rodent-like creature that lived and made its lair in the lower levels of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. These creatures, though fearsome in appearance, tended to be skittish and solitary by nature. It had tusks, spines, and claws that were strong enough to dig through [[Ferrocrete/Legends|ferroconcrete]].

